    "We use the smotefamily package implemented in R for sampling during training.",
    "The crucial parameter for solving real-life problems with machine learning is making the model explainable if decision makers want to use the information obtained for interventions.",
    "An accurate model alone is useless if it remains a black box, and we cannot explain to decision makers the antecedents of leavers' past decisions.",
    "There are several research that aims to provide explanations and it is one of the most important research areas in recent years because explainability increases confidence in the results.",
    "Establishing explainability has started with several ideas."
